659
00:28:36,060 --> 00:28:38,040
- Well, we love walking our dog,

660
00:28:38,040 --> 00:28:40,588
so we walk in for at
least an hour every day.

661
00:28:40,588 --> 00:28:43,799
I also have a stationary
bike and a treadmill,

662
00:28:43,799 --> 00:28:45,347
which is great for winter

663
00:28:45,347 --> 00:28:48,120
because I don't have to
go outside when it's cold.

664
00:28:48,120 --> 00:28:51,030
- [Will] 97, do you have
any guilty pleasures

