00:29:03,806 --> 00:29:07,620
- I love collapsing on
the sofa with my husband,

671
00:29:07,620 --> 00:29:12,620
my dog, and my cat, and
watching a predictable movie.

672
00:29:13,530 --> 00:29:16,704
- [Will] 99, what's one
activity or practise you do

